-----Register New User Test-----

1. Open my.hideez.com in browser
2. Click "Register" button
3. Enter "Test Name" in first name field
4. Enter "Test Surname" in last name field
5. Enter test.user.mail@gmail.com in email field
6. Enter "12345678" in password field
7. Enter "12345678" in confirm password field
8. Click "Submit" button

Expected result:
Message that user should approve his email appeared, user can login in system with this credentials





